# Installation

@container install
@row install-flow
  @card
    ## Install CLI
    `npm install -g marque`
  @end card

  @card
    ## Init project
    `marque new docs`
  @end card

  @card
    ## Run dev server
    `marque serve docs`
  @end card
@end row install-flow
@end container install
